      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive double-VANOS overhaul. The suspension geometry remains precise with refreshed bushings, while the engine maintains a linear power delivery and exceptional throttle response. Though it exhibits minor cosmetic patina consistent with spirited use, the drivetrain and chassis integrity make it an ideal candidate for the discerning enthusiast seeking a visceral driving experience.",
